Last year Miss Jolie and Mr Hague travelled together to  the Democratic Republic of Congo, where they met survivors of rape.

Their visit to Sarajevo comes ten weeks ahead of the three-day Global Summit to End Sexual Violence in Conflict, which they will chair in London in June.

