'We can and must change the entire global attitude to these crimes, and shatter the culture of impunity.'

Miss Jolie and Mr Hague will meet survivors of sexual violence from the war in Bosnia, which ran between 1992 and 1995, as well as judges and prosecutors in the country who are working to address the huge backlog of sexual violence cases.

